[TITLE_SPANISH]Ferrita L1
[TITLE_ENGLISH]L1 Ferrite

[BLOCK_START]
[BEGIN_LIST]
[SPANISH]La ferrita <b>L1</b> conecta la masa del conector USB con el chasis.
[ENGLISH]The <b>L1</b> ferrite connects the ground of the USB connector with the chassis.
[END_LIST]
[IMG]01.png
[BLOCK_END]

[BLOCK_START]
[BEGIN_LIST]
[SPANISH]Esta es la ferrita recomendada en el diseño de referencia de Arduino. El fabricante es <b>Murata</b> y el part number es <b>BLM21PG600SN1D</b>
[ENGLISH]This is the recommended ferrite in the Arduino reference design. The manufacturer is <b>Murata</b> and the part number is <b>BLM21PG600SN1D</b>
[END_LIST]
[IMG]02.png
[IMG]03.png
[BLOCK_END]

[BLOCK_START]
[BEGIN_LIST]
[SPANISH]En la librería <b>Device</b> he encontrado el símbolo <b>Ferrite_Bead_Small</b>
[ENGLISH]In the library <b>Device</b> I found the symbol <b>Ferrite_Bead_Small</b>
[END_LIST]
[IMG]04.png

[BEGIN_LIST]
[SPANISH]Lo he copiado en la librería <b>JAVIERM_LIBS</b> y le he añadido los campos habituales en mis diseños.
[ENGLISH]I have copied it in the <b>JAVIERM_LIBS</b> library and added the usual fields in my designs.
[END_LIST]
[IMG]05.png
[BLOCK_END]

