[BLOCK_START]
[BEGIN_LIST]
[SPANISH]En las librerías de KiCad no he encontrado un footprint para una ferrita de encapsulado 0805, pero el del condensador nos sirve. Ya que como ves el símbolo de KiCad es algo mayor que lo que recomienda el datasheet.
[ENGLISH]In the KiCad libraries I have not found a footprint for a 0805 package ferrite, but the one for the capacitor works for us. Since as you can see the KiCad symbol is somewhat larger than what the datasheet recommends.
[END_LIST]
[IMG]07.png
[IMG]08.png

